metadata.name: WarmlyRush
metadata.description:
Warmly Rush 2022

2208 X 1242px  300 PPP

Before all this is over we are going to enjoy and enjoy what we have dance and really feel it  be aware and value every second that we live seek our dreams and be part of the beautiful and cozy home that we decide to create for the hole world 

Inspired artwork in the power of feelings and capacity to transcend and transmit a message of hope

*this artwork includes a Timelapse video of the process*

Luko
